{
  "id": "virtualchest",
  "name": "VirtualChest",
  "author": "Blugin",
  "description": "A plugin give virtual chest to player for PocketMine-MP",
  "readme_markdown": "<p>A plugin give virtual chest to player for PocketMine-MP</p>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-command\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#command\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Command</h2>\n<p>Main command : <code>/vchest &lt;open | default | set | lang | reload | save&gt;</code></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>subcommand</th>\n<th>arguments</th>\n<th>description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Open</td>\n<td>[chest number]</td>\n<td>Open my virtual chest</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Set</td>\n<td>&lt;player name&gt; &lt;chest count&gt;</td>\n<td>Set player's chest count</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Default</td>\n<td>&lt;chest count&gt;</td>\n<td>Set default chest count</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>View</td>\n<td>&lt;player name&gt; [chest number]</td>\n<td>Open player's virtual chest</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Lang</td>\n<td>&lt;language prefix&gt;</td>\n<td>Load default lang file</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Reload</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>Reload all data</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Save</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>Save all data</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-permission\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#permission\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Permission</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>permission</th>\n<th>default</th>\n<th>description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>vchest.cmd</td>\n<td>USER</td>\n<td>main command</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>vchest.cmd.open</td>\n<td>USER</td>\n<td>open subcommand</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>vchest.cmd.set</td>\n<td>OP</td>\n<td>set  subcommand</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>vchest.cmd.default</td>\n<td>OP</td>\n<td>default subcommand</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>vchest.cmd.view</td>\n<td>OP</td>\n<td>view subcommand</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>vchest.cmd.lang</td>\n<td>OP</td>\n<td>lang subcommand</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>vchest.cmd.reload</td>\n<td>OP</td>\n<td>reload subcommand</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>vchest.cmd.save</td>\n<td>OP</td>\n<td>save subcommand</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-changelog\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#changelog\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>ChangeLog</h2>\n<h3>\n<a id=\"user-content-v100--\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#v100--\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>v1.0.0 <a href=\"https://github.com/PMMPPlugin/VirtualChest/tree/v1.0.0\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/a65ccd17383fe6f47cd26b66cd8710a1b603fb20/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f62616467652f736f757263652d76312e302e302d626c75652e706e673f6c6162656c3d736f75726365\" alt=\"Source\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/source-v1.0.0-blue.png?label=source\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a> <a href=\"https://github.com/PMMPPlugin/VirtualChest/releases/v1.0.0\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/0ff52ba21b571f0b991c3babad1324b51eb97bb3/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769746875622f646f776e6c6f6164732f504d4d50506c7567696e2f5669727475616c43686573742f76312e302e302f746f74616c2e706e673f6c6162656c3d646f776e6c6f616426636f6c6f72423d316661646164\" alt=\"Release\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/downloads/PMMPPlugin/VirtualChest/v1.0.0/total.png?label=download&amp;colorB=1fadad\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>First release</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3>\n<a id=\"user-content-v101--\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#v101--\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>v1.0.1 <a href=\"https://github.com/PMMPPlugin/VirtualChest/tree/v1.0.1\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/a000364ddaf96daaf6b5f2a13f1db78a68504d9c/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f62616467652f736f757263652d76312e302e312d626c75652e706e673f6c6162656c3d736f75726365\" alt=\"Source\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.